==English==
{{Wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From [[French]] ''argent''; from [[Latin]] ''argentum'' "white money", "silver".

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ˈaːdʒent/}}
*{{IPA|/ˈɑɹdʒent/}}

===Noun===
'''argent'''
# [[silver]]
#(''colour'') the white or silver colour on a coat of arms.
#:<table><tr><td>argent colour: &nbsp;</td><td bgcolor="#848482" width="80">&nbsp; </td></tr></table>

